{"id": "1171413060473323551", "channel_id": "1171413060473323551", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天米爾拿到了獨家爆料噢！！\n看看你猜對了嗎？今天要介紹的是【血肉界域】！胚胎、心臟、吞噬、融合，哪一個關鍵詞能戳中你呢~\n（據說，血肉界域的喚醒體，都很喜歡以小博大，你會不會是其中一個呢？）\n\n血肉界域天賦 -「猩紅獻祭」\n*回合開始時獲得一定胚胎融合進度，\n   達到100%時將1張「胚胎」置入手牌。\n\n*打出胚胎能夠選擇喚醒體增加狂氣，\n   血肉界域的「狂氣爆發」會消耗胚胎觸發吞噬效果。", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T11:37:17.419000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😂", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1171413060896968796", "filename": "SPOILER_download_3.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1809236, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171413060473323551/1171413060896968796/SPOILER_download_3.png?ex=69cbb1ed&is=69ca606d&hm=a4f847e6a329a4dd6b9568f9bebfe3c23adf09c73d197197ed0737fd6d1e0f06&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171413060473323551", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「血肉界域」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171417112930172939", "channel_id": "1171413060473323551", "type": 4, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "「血肉界域」介紹", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T11:53:23.600000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171413060473323551", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「血肉界域」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171396762716614717", "channel_id": "1171396762716614717", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家看看這張圖，猜猜這個是什麼呢？\n\nA.碎裂的面具  B.開心和不開心  C.混沌界域  D.我有其他想法", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T10:32:31.731000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-08T02:31:02.746000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1171396762892771338", "filename": "5f074ef5-96c8-4bc5-a8c8-1500fbc6c701_1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 167757, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171396762716614717/1171396762892771338/5f074ef5-96c8-4bc5-a8c8-1500fbc6c701_1.png?ex=69cba2bf&is=69ca513f&hm=d74954085076cc6ce9883b21a41201b2ffc0cc62352f6de504647f372d22cd15&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171396762716614717", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「混沌界域」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171396808526790687", "channel_id": "1171396762716614717", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "答案是 C.混沌界域\n\n彌薩格大學通過研究災難的衍生物——銀芯，賦予了逝者超越人類的力量，從而使其成為了喚醒體，\n而這些超越人類的力量，分別來自於不同的界域，其中大部分來自於混沌界域、深海界域、血肉界域、超維界域。不同的喚醒體，是從不同的界域中獲得他們的能力的。\n\n\n現在已經出現過的喚醒體已經有6個啦！大家都知道哪些是混沌界域的嗎？\n**截止2023年11月2日，包含在Facebook已經公佈的拉蒙拉、朵爾、奧吉爾，以及預約頁面上大家也能聽到過聲音的蘿坦、朵爾、拉蒙娜、奧瑞塔、尤烏哈希，一共是6個喚醒體哦~**\n\n答案：蘿坦、朵爾、拉蒙娜、奧吉爾，都是混沌界域的哦！\n奧瑞塔是深海界域，尤烏哈希是血肉界域哦~", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T10:32:42.653000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-16T08:13:48.370000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171396762716614717", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「混沌界域」介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
