{"id": "1171412455751176272", "channel_id": "1171412455751176272", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "「深海」界域前來報道！\n其能使用觸腕攻擊敵人\n並且愈戰愈強\n*小貼士：每當敵人死亡時，觸腕傷害也會提升\n而奧瑞塔承載著「深海」界域之力\n也在向各位守密人問好~\n各位守密人猜猜一下哪種行為能夠提高奧瑞塔的好感度呢~\n\nA.帶奧瑞塔去彌薩格大學上課。\nB.每日10點喚醒奧瑞塔。\nC.與奧瑞塔成為夥伴。", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T11:34:53.242000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1171412458150305792", "filename": "3ad71463-0545-4d79-ac61-4b52854b31ec.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 9561182, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1171412455751176272/1171412458150305792/3ad71463-0545-4d79-ac61-4b52854b31ec.png?ex=69cbb15d&is=69ca5fdd&hm=cdc9a2aa9333dab40a156842a3e3ec9c07371d9fd66a5c39e137dae543c6d38a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171412455751176272", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海界域「奧瑞塔」喚醒體介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
{"id": "1171412968974585886", "channel_id": "1171412455751176272", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "A.畢竟是小孩子，奧瑞塔很害怕去彌薩格大學上課喔！\n\nB.奧瑞塔喚醒的最佳時間其實是每早7點，這樣就可以陪伴奧瑞塔去海邊撿貝殼啦！\n\nC.沒錯啦~奧瑞塔最喜歡交朋友啦~各位守密人，答應我請與奧瑞塔成為一生的好夥伴！", "timestamp": "2023-11-07T11:36:55.604000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🇦", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🇧", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🇨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1171412455751176272", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海界域「奧瑞塔」喚醒體介紹", "forum_channel_id": "1171394049970798602", "thread_tags": ["1171395309264453674"]}
